            <td colspan="2" class="titulo2" valign="top">
              Jewishness in the Fiction of Ir&egrave;ne N&eacute;mirovsky<span
 class="texto2"> by <a href="../../issue11/sarah-glazer/bio.php"
 class="link3">Sarah Glazer</a></span></td>
            <td>&nbsp;</td>
